CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Sila Realty Trust Inc is a real estate investment trust. Its investment objective is to pay regular cash distributions to stockholders and to preserve, protect, and return capital contributions to stockholders. The company owns and manages healthcare assets. Its operating segment includes Data Center and Healthcare. The company generates maximum revenue from the Healthcare segment.
